description:
Rewrite the traditional "Hello World" program using the modern **Implicit Main** syntax.

Traditional:
```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Hello, Modern Java!");
    }
}
```

Rewrite it to use `void main()`.

